PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2023-08832023-09-07PMO
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Inquiry under the name of the Public Inquiry into Foreign Interference in Federal Electoral Processes and Democratic Institutions as a Department and the Prime Minister as the Appropriate Minister
PrecisOrder (1) designating the Commission named the PUBLIC INQUIRY INTO FOREIGN INTERFERENCE IN FEDERAL ELECTORAL PROCESSES AND DEMOCRATIC INSTITUTIONS as a department for the purposes of the Act; and (2) designating the Prime Minister as the appropriate Minister with respect to the Commission.
